                Mr. Manningham-Buller
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f520746d-4821-45c2-9c17-53abcb1225f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-03-21/debates/709d9315-19b9-4f2d-bc51-1c8453182363/WarDamage(IncreaseOfValuePayments)Order#contribution-f520746d-4821-45c2-9c17-53abcb1225f1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
